websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tin vui cho m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t CLB \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Everton, Tottenham hay Borussia Dortmund.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Zaha \u0111\u1eaft h\u00e0ng tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWilfried Zaha tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. Anh g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United mua v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2013 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV David Moyes, Zaha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. Anh b\u1ecb \u0111em cho Cardiff m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a 2013/14. Ngay sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i cho CLB c\u0169 Crystal Palace.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/15/Zaha-muon-roi-Crystal-Palace-va-tu-choi-gia-han-hop-dong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi Wilfried Zaha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n4 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, Zaha v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh gi\u00fap Palace \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Zaha l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn h\u01a1n Palace. Nh\u1eefng Everton, Tottenham hay Borussia Dortmund \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u0169i c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 m\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB n\u00e0y. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Palace \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Zaha k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 125 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng anh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Wilfried Zaha\" title=\"tien ve Wilfried Zaha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nZaha cho hay quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng. C\u1ed1t l\u00f5i l\u00e0 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n 26, Zaha tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf CLB l\u1edbn m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Zaha v\u1edbi Palace c\u00f2n t\u1edbi 4 n\u0103m v\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i. Nghe \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng NHA tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-chia-tay-sterling-172-191666.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-liverpool-danh-bai-chelsea-vu-alisson-172-191664.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 Alisson</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191654.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-courois-172-191653.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1453","checkdouble":"191673"},{"date":"17:16 20/07","title":"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sao tr\u1ebb MU sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Club America","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/mourinho-khen-ngoi-dac-biet-sao-tre-tahith-chong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 khen ng\u1ee3i sao tr\u1ebb Tahith Chong sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa Man United v\u00e0 Club America h\u00f4m nay.</h2><h2>Tahith Chong ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Juan Mata. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-1 sau khi Man United b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTahith Chong l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 Herrera b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng d\u1ed9i c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Mata s\u00fat b\u1ed3i tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Club America.</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Chong\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Tahith Chong sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Club America h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Tahith Chong sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Club America h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/mourinho-khen-ngoi-dac-biet-sao-tre-tahith-chong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Tahith Chong sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Club America</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-club-america-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191627.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Club America vs MU</span>, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man United, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 18 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTahith Chong ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. V\u00e0 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cQu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mata l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n m\u00e0 Chong \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin khi ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cD\u1eabu v\u1eady, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng khi v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n c\u00f3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t\".</em></div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMourinho l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho sao tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng Chong c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t Man United \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. B\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u1edf h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t c\u00f2n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 mong manh v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1452","checkdouble":"191675"},{"date":"16:13 20/07","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-alisson-toi-liverpool.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Jurgen Klopp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, song c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua sau v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua sau v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/4-nguoi-thang-va-3-nguoi-thua-sau-vu-Liverpool-mua-Alisson-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp vui m\u1eebng khi Alisson c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Mignolet ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00ec Karius l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd. S\u1ee9c \u00e9p qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1eafc 2 sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 v\u1edbi Real Madrid khi\u1ebfn Liverpool thua 1-3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Jurgen Klopp hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o hai th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Ngay sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1 2018 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi v\u00e0 Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span>. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Kop \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng, h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung t\u1eeb Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita c\u00f2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u00eam Alisson, Liverpool h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. HLV Klopp \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson t\u1eeb Roma khi\u1ebfn hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Anfield.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loris Karius Simon Mignolet Jurgen Klopp\" title=\"Loris Karius Simon Mignolet Jurgen Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/Liverpool-chieu-mo-Alisson-Ho-da-co-De-Gea-cua-rieng-minh!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb khi Liverpool \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMignolet l\u00fac n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch ra \u0111i. Napoli \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Mignolet m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi Karius, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 FA Cup hay c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Virgil Van Dijk v\u00e0 Dejan Lovren</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i b\u0103ng ra kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Dijk va Lovren se nhan duoc su ho tro rat lon tu Alisson\" title=\"Van Dijk v\u00e0 Lovren s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/lovren.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Van Dijk v\u00e0 Lovren s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Alisson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Manuel Neuer c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Ederson hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City.&nbsp;V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u0103ng ra d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7&nbsp; Virgil Van Dijk v\u00e0&nbsp;Dejan Lovren.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVirgil Van Dijk th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh. V\u1edbi Dejan Lovren, anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson trong khung g\u1ed7, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m t\u1eeb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Virgil Van Dijk v\u00e0 Dejan Lovren.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Real Madrid, Don Balon th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Los Blancos \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Alisson nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u thay th\u1ebf Courtois.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"sarri\" title=\"sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-chi-ra-vi-tri-yeu-nhat-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Sarri c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Conte, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Roma. Kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alisson ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992, tuy nhi\u00ean Alisson \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Anfield thay v\u00ec Stamford Bridge. Alisson mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Klopp v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Salah thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alisson, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Jan Oblak (Atletico Madrid) ho\u1eb7c Jasper Cillessen (Barca), song kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 The Blues c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Kasper Schmeichel</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Alisson kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Kasper Schmeichel c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kasper Schmeichel co the khoac ao Chelsea thay Courtois\" title=\"Kasper Schmeichel c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea thay Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/kas.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kasper Schmeichel c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea thay Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKasper Schmeichel n\u0103m nay 32 tu\u1ed5i, anh ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Leicester v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a 2015/16.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Leicester c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 HLV Sarri d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao, m\u1ea5t Riyad Mahrez khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd y\u1ebfu \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Kasper Schmeichel c\u00f9ng Leicester h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Chelsea ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kasper Schmeichel, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng 3 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp The Blues \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh t\u1eeb Leicester. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 Danny Drinkwater, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa l\u00e0 Kante c\u00f2n H\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Everton</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nghe c\u00f3 v\u1ebb v\u00f4 l\u00fd b\u1edfi Everton \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu Jordan Pickford \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Everton ch\u1ecbu thua Roma trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma voi so tien thu ve tu viec ban Alisson co the vuot mat Everton vu Malcom\" title=\"Roma v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n Alisson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Everton v\u1ee5 Malcom\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/malcom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n Alisson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Everton v\u1ee5 Malcom</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEverton \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u1ea5t trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, song m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 n\u1ebfu Roma v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoma t\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Malcom v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 40 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 Bordeaux \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thu v\u1ec1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Olympico l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Everton \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Roma v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. Theo \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Malcom mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Roma</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2 n\u0103m 2016, Roma ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Olympico, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Wojciech Szczesny. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, khi m\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus Alisson m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Day thu mon Alisson den Liverpool, Monchi mang ve den 12 tan binh cho AS Roma he nay.\" title=\"\u0110\u1ea9y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool, Monchi mang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ebfn 12 t\u00e2n binh cho AS Roma h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/monchi-1.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb v\u1ee5 Alisson, Roma d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i khi ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, anh gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 17/37 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Serie A. T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00ean t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 80%, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoma \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Alisson cho Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 b\u00e1n anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ch\u1ec9 sau 2 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Alisson m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng n\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 9 b\u00e0n thua trong 2 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 v\u1edbi Liverpool.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool d\u00ednh ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa l\u1eeba th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi Roma, v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil h\u1ecd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1451","checkdouble":"191677"},{"date":"16:45 20/07","title":"Sao Chelsea nh\u1eafn nh\u1ee7 Hazard: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n anh!\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/fabregas-phat-bieu-ve-hazard-dong-doi-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hazard, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n anh tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Anh c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p 1-0. Hazard c\u0169ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 2 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian qua, nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin Real Madrid li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Hazard ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hazard Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n anh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hazard Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n anh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Fabregas-phat-bieu-ve-Hazard-Chung-toi-can-anh!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea ngay sau World Cup</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00f3 tin Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt khi ngay sau World Cup, anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fabregas n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n ph\u00eda l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 Hazard. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hazard cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i nh\u1eb1m ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabregas va Hazard tai chelsea\" title=\"Fabregas va Hazard tai chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/fabregas-phat-bieu-ve-hazard-dong-doi-tai-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fabregas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hazard v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i d\u1ed1i, t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Hazard\u201d, Fabregas chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i CLB v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u1ea7n gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y y\u00eau m\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19 v\u00e0 Hazard c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ea5m poster qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m gia t\u0103ng ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 The Blues r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-doi-dembele-lay-hazard-184-191575.html\">Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 l\u1ea5y Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-chelsea-neu-hazard-muon-ra-di-toi-se-khong-can-duong-172-191562.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea: \u201cN\u1ebfu Hazard mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-bo-chelsea-sang-real-madrid-172-191484.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard b\u1ecf Chelsea sang Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-quyet-dau-voi-real-vi-eden-hazard-180-191467.html\">Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real v\u00ec Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1450","checkdouble":"191678"},{"date":"16:40 20/07","title":"Keylor Navas kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/keylor-navas-khong-ngai-canh-tranh-vi-tri-voi-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Keylor Navas v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, song Real v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Thibaut Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Keylor Navas n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Keylor Navas n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Thibaut-Courtois-toi-Real-Madrid,-Keylor-Navas-noi-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real mua Thibaut Courtois th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra 35 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaily Mail th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Courtois \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, The Blues bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThe Blues l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-courois-172-191653.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea nh\u1eafm 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thay th\u1ebf Courtois</span>, bao g\u1ed3m Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan, Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ee7a Leicester City v\u00e0 Petr Cech c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Courtois, Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea5t Eden Hazard v\u00e0o tay Real Madrid. C\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Keylor Navas tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Keylor Navas n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Keylor Navas n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/keylor-navas-khong-ngai-canh-tranh-vi-tri-voi-courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Keylor Navas quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAS kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Navas quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ra \u0111i, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef v\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real c\u00f2n Keylor Navas kh\u00f4ng ra \u0111i, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kiko Casilla s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi b\u1edfi anh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n khi \u0111\u1ea5u khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1449","checkdouble":"191679"},{"date":"10:38 20/07","title":"L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a HLV Wenger","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/lo-ben-do-cuc-soc-cua-hlv-wenger.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Wenger</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi chia tay Arsenal sau h\u01a1n 20 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, HLV Wenger v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 68 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"R\u1eddi Arsenal, HLV Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"R\u1eddi Arsenal, HLV Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/lo-ben-do-cuc-soc-cua-hlv-wenger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Wenger v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Theo Daily Mail, Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m nay, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Vahid Halilhodzic (ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia) v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Akira Nishino. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 63 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf hoa Anh \u0111\u00e0o v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, song c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i 3-2. D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Akira Nishino \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t HLV n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Wenger nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 HLV Wenger l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Wenger t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 m\u00f9a 1995/96 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB Nagoya Grampus Eight c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, sau khi r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u00f4ng m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wenger\" title=\"Wenger\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/15/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-16-chu-tu-wenger-se-thay-the-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Wenger c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn, Iniesta v\u00e0 Fernando Torres \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc x\u1ee9 s\u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u00f4ng Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110TQG n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1448","checkdouble":"191651"},{"date":"11:06 20/07","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ed1t 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/chelsea-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-courois.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKeylor Navas v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, song n\u0103m nay anh \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n. Thibaut Courtois \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Chelsea nh\u1eafm n\u1ebfu Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Chelsea nh\u1eafm n\u1ebfu Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/chelsea-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-courois.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thibaut Courtois s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Courtois \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb dao \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu. C\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Madrid, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i TBN \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ed1t ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma\" title=\"Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Milan-muon-doi-Donnarumma-lay-Morata-cua-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gianluigi Donnarumma \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm thay Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEvening Standard kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh danh s\u00e1ch 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Chelsea bao g\u1ed3m Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan, Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ee7a\u00a0Leicester City v\u00e0 Petr Cech c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/khong-the-gay-soc-vu-alisson-chelsea-chuyen-huong-sang-donnarumma-172-191596.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Donnarumma</span>, n\u1ebfu AC Milan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Kasper Schmeichel. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Leicester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d gi\u1eef th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 Chelsea s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i mua l\u1ea1i Petr Cech, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Donnarumma, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng Alvaro Morata trao \u0111\u1ed5i. The Blues s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan nh\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 19 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1447","checkdouble":"191653"},{"date":"11:28 20/07","title":"\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Mexico. Juan Mata l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap M.U tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Mexico. Juan Mata l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap M.U tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</h2>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Sergio Romero, Joel Pereira, Lee Grant<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Antonio Valencia, Matteo Darmian, Diogo Dalot, Timothy  Fosu-Mensah, RoShaun Williams, Chris Smalling, Eric Bailly, Axel  Tuanzebe, Demetri Mitchell, Luke Shaw<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: James Garner, Ander Herrera, Andreas Pereira, Scott McTominay, Ethan Hamilton<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Tahith Chong, Angel Gomes, Juan Mata, Anthony Martial, Mason Greenwood, Joshua Bohui.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-club-america-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191627.html\">MU 1-1 Club America (KT): Juan Mata c\u1ee9u Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf h\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-don-tin-cuc-vui-ve-alexis-sanchez-172-191630.html\">M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin c\u1ef1c vui v\u1ec1 Alexis Sanchez</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibra-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-buoc-phai-roi-mu-172-191638.html\">Ibra ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1446","checkdouble":"191654"},{"date":"10:49 20/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League: \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA \u2013 HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/14/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 20 V-League 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ed3n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><h2>\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB HAGL s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c mang t\u00ean SLNA tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a NHM b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi su\u1ed1t 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1eady, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u0169ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 13 cho t\u1edbi nay. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 4 tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/14/truoc-tran-hagl-vs-slna-chuyen-gia-mach-nuoc-cho-doi-bong-xu-nghe.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;SLNA vs HAGL l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i&nbsp;v\u00f2ng 20 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda HAGL, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 &lsquo;y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng v\u00eda&rsquo; khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u00fang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y khi &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Thanh H\u00f3a hay b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t SLNA ch\u1ec9 &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1ea1ng&rsquo;, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i trong l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i SLNA v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1edbi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 &ldquo;hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00ec l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang sa s\u00fat sau chu\u1ed7i 10 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 13 tr\u00ean BXH v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t v\u00e0 x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH. Do \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u nay, XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 &ldquo;chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111ang x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m (17 so v\u1edbi 16). V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn b\u1ee9t l\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e1y BXH. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n nay, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi m\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 &ldquo;l\u1ea5n&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Can Tho vs Sai Gon\" title=\"C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Thanh H\u00f3a c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League n\u0103m nay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd v\u1eabn b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1edbi 14 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y l\u00ean ng\u00f4i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 b\u1ecb ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. Thanh H\u00f3a l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng tuy nhi\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c sau nh\u1eefng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a d\u00e0n sao tr\u1ebb Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Ki\u00ean, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0103n Th\u00e1i Qu\u00fd.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thanh hoa vs Ha Noi\" title=\"thanh h\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/anh1_1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thanh H\u00f3a \u1edf 3 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng, Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1i sau 5 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, d\u00f9 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi Thanh H\u00f3a trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 0-3 ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 CLB TP.HCM vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bongda24h s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 20 V-League 2018\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Vong-20-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018-344-191652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018-344-191652.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 17h00 ng\u00e0y 20/7 (V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 20/7 (V\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1445","checkdouble":"191655"},{"date":"11:16 20/07","title":"Neymar ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/neymar-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi PSG d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb CLB Real Madrid.</h2><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">Neymar l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">\u00a0<br>\r\n</span>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Neymar l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Neymar-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Neymar t\u00e1i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi CLB PSG trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi chia tay si\u00eau sao Ronaldo, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf CR7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 Neymar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Los Blancos nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 \u2018ve v\u00e3n\u2019 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Fox Sports trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 l\u00e0m t\u1eeb thi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat PSG cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch cao h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. D\u01b0 lu\u1eadn th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Real nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u1eafc c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m t\u00f4i d\u00e0nh cho PSG l\u1edbn bi\u1ebft nh\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1c, t\u1edd AS th\u00e2n CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft HLV m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a PSG l\u00e0 \u00f4ng Tuchel kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1eafm v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf World Cup, v\u00e0 \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a PSG xoay quanh sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe.\u00a0V\u00ec th\u1ebf PSG ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb Los Blancos.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Roboto-Regular, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-van-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-neymar-180-191642.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/6/real-madrid-van-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-neymar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-van-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-neymar-180-191642.html\">Real Madrid v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mua Neymar th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-neymar-da-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-197-191453.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/17/psg-neymar-da-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-neymar-da-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-197-191453.html\">PSG: Neymar \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span><br>\r\nLuis Fernandez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/effenberg-so-sanh-mandzukic-va-neymar-421-191231.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/effenberg-so-sanh-mandzukic-va-neymar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/effenberg-so-sanh-mandzukic-va-neymar-421-191231.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c: T\u00f4i th\u00edch Mandzukic g\u1ea5p 10 Neymar</span><br>\r\nEffenberg so s\u00e1nh Mandzukic v\u00e0 Neymar. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u1eebng danh tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Mario Mandzukic s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 200 tri\u1ec7u Euro.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nThanh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1444","checkdouble":"191656"},{"date":"11:02 20/07","title":"Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 1-1 Club America (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/video-tong-hop-mu-11-club-america-giao-huu-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; paddin